"""
        Test that the a PermissionDenied error is raised if multiple possible
        client identities are discovered.
        """
mock_get.return_value = ['John Doe', 'Jane Doe']
args = 'test',
self.assertRaisesRegex(exceptions.PermissionDenied,
    'Multiple client identities found.', utils.
    get_client_identity_from_certificate, *args)
mock.patch('kmip.services.server.auth.utils.get_common_names_from_certificate')
